Type of Information
How Do We Use It?
To use KID Mode App and related services, you as parent will be required to
create an Account
. During the registration flow you will be requested to provide us with a valid email address as well as choose your Account’s designated parent password.
We will use this information for the purpose of performing our contract with the parent, provide the requested Services, and designate the Account through which you will be able to access the dashboard and use the tools provided therein. We will also use the email address in order to send the parent needed information related to our Services and additional occasional promotional communications related to the Services, as well as verify your identity.
To create the child(ren)’s “
KID Profile
” you as parent will be requested to provide your child’s gender, first name and birth month and year.
We will use such information to personalize the child’s experience, including providing direct access to third-party apps and content that we find to be appropriate and relevant for the child, based on age and language.
If you
contact us
for support or other inquiries through any means of communication available in our Services you will be required to provide us with a valid email address and may provide us with your name.
We will use this information solely for the purpose of responding to your inquiries directly on a one-time basis and providing you with the support you have requested.
