means the section of the Online Services Interface where KIDOZ provides Publisher access to curated Online Services Data displaying performance of the Ads served on Publisher Prepared Media.
Publisher Prepared Media –
means any App, CTV Content, or Website that either includes the KIDOZ SDK, utilizes tags provided by KIDOZ, or connects to the Online Services via OpenRTB or other communication protocol.
